<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">ACTS (CM)</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cm_1</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">Even though we live in a democracy, a few people will always run things anyway.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">ACTS (CM)</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cm_2</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">The people who really run the country are not known to the voters.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">ACTS (CM)</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cm_3</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">Big events like wars, the current recession, and the outcomes of elections are controlled by small groups of people who are working in secret against the rest of us.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">ACTS (CM)</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cm_4</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">Much of our lives are being controlled by plots hatched in secret places.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">CB</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cb_1</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">Jeffrey Epstein, the billionaire accused of running an elite sex trafficking ring, was murdered to cover-up the activities of his criminal network.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">CB</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cb_2</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">The U.S. government is mandating the switch to compact fluorescent light bulbs because such lights make people more obedient and easier to control.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">CB</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cb_3</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">The Food and Drug Administration is deliberately preventing the public from getting natural cures for cancer and other diseases because of pressure from drug companies.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">CB</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cb_4</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">Billionaire George Soros is behind a hidden plot to destabilize the American government, take control of the media, and put the world under his control.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">CB</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cb_5</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">Bill Gates is behind the coronavirus pandemic.</td>
</tr>
